Implemented “ultra mode” behavior for Leha.

What changed:

Added assistant_core.py, a fast local intent layer.
stop, pause, next, previous, volume up/down are handled locally before the LLM.
stop / pause can work without saying Leha.
open chrome, play music, etc. still require Leha or an active conversation window.
